---
description: Auto commit and push project changes to GitHub after code edits
alwaysApply: true
---

After completing any code changes in this project:

1. Run git sync using the project Git executable:
   `"C:\Program Files\Git\bin\git.exe"` in `C:\Users\USER\Desktop\AI_team_takura-main`
2. Stage all changes: `git add -A` (never commit `.env` — it is gitignored)
3. Commit with a clear message describing what changed and why
4. Push to `origin main` on `https://github.com/takuraanigatsuki-hub/AI_team_takura`
5. If push fails, report the error — do not skip silently

Remote: `https://github.com/takuraanigatsuki-hub/AI_team_takura.git`
